  "title": "Bookkeeper & Accounting – Accounts & Documentation",
  "description": "<p><strong>Bookkeeper & Accounting – Accounts & Documentation</strong></p><h3><strong>Role Overview:</strong></h3><p>We are seeking a reliable and detail-driven professional to manage bookkeeping, accounting support, and financial documentation. This role will handle daily financial records, assist with accounting processes, and ensure accurate, compliant documentation across the business.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Maintain day-to-day bookkeeping including income, expenses, and general ledger entries</p></li><li><p>Manage accounts payable and receivable</p></li><li><p>Perform bank and account reconciliations</p></li><li><p>Assist with accounting entries, journal postings, and trial balance preparation</p></li><li><p>Support month-end and year-end accounting close</p></li><li><p>Prepare and maintain financial records for audits, tax filings, and compliance</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper filing and organization of invoices, receipts, and statutory documents</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with external accountants, auditors, and tax consultants</p></li><li><p>Monitor discrepancies and support financial accuracy and controls</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements & Skills:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Experience in bookkeeping and accounting support roles</p></li><li><p>Working knowledge of accounting principles and financial statements</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in accounting software and Excel</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and documentation skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Clear communication and coordination skills</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Preferred Qualifications:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field</p></li><li><p>Experience with tax preparation support and compliance</p></li><li><p>Exposure to cloud-based accounting systems</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Hands-on role with real ownership of accounts</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to grow into a broader accounting function</p></li><li><p>Supportive and collaborative work culture</p></li></ul>",
